The charges brought by the Anti-Mafia Directorate in Calabria against Mayor and Deputy Mayor Gioia Tauro Giorgi Dal Torrione e Rosario Schiavone and Mayor Rosarna Carla Martelli, who was detained this morning for external cooperation with the Mafia organization, are grave.
In the tracks also Gioacchino Piromalli, an old mediator between the clan and the public administration, and his grandson a lawyer, the nominee of the boss, already accused of committing crimes of a mafia character, sentenced to pay 10 million euros.
